    significant physiological and psychological impacts. Recognizing its subtle
    beginnings and understanding its progression is the first step toward
    reclaiming your well-being. It's crucial to acknowledge that while
    individual resilience is important, systemic factors within workplaces often
    contribute significantly to the problem.
  </p>
